JO  - The Review of Financial Studies
JA  - Rev Financ Stud
VL  - 5
IS  - 2
SP  - 281
EP  - 305
SN  - 0893-9454
AB  - I investigate the empirical importance of information revelation in the pricing of block trades. In particular, I examine whether block prices are correlated with the unexpected part of firms’ quarterly earnings. For my sample of block trades, information revelation does indeed appear to be a significant factor shortly before earnings announcements.
Y2  - 3/26/2024
